headline: OMS Energy Technologies Inc. Celebrates Nasdaq Listing with Opening Bell Ceremony, Highlighting Post-IPO Momentum and Growth
summary: SINGPORE, Aug. 28, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- OMS Energy Technologies Inc. (“OMS” or the “Company”) (NASDAQ: OMSE), a growth-oriented manufacturer of surface wellhead systems (“SWS”) and oil country tubular goods (“OCTG”) for the oil and gas industry, today rang the Opening Bell at the Nasdaq MarketSite in Times Square to celebrate its successful initial public offering on May 13, 2025, and its legacy of over 50 years of service to the energy sector. Credit: Nasdaq, Inc. / Vanja Savic Mr. How Meng
